com.google.api.gax.grpc

Class GrpcApiExceptionFactory

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.google.api.gax.grpc.GrpcApiExceptionFactory

  • @BetaApi
public class GrpcApiExceptionFactory
extends java.lang.Object
    A factory class that returns the corresponding type of exception class from the given status code.

    For more information about the status codes returned by the underlying grpc exception see https://github.com/grpc/grpc-java/blob/master/core/src/main/java/io/grpc/Status.java
